T(t)
\frac{T'}{T}=\frac{X''}{X}=\lambda \text{ where } \lambda = -\beta^{2}\\ X(x)=c_{1}\cos(\beta x)+c_{2}\sin(\beta x) \\ \Rightarrow \beta=n \\ \Rightarrow\lambda=-(n)^{2} \\ X_{n}=\sin(nx)
 T'+ n^{2}T=0 \\ T_{n}(t)=e^{-n^{2}t} \\ X(x)T(t)=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}e^{-n^{2}t}\sin(nx)
t=0
